Performs tasks specific to Fedora stabilized repository in RDO, as removing
official Fedora repositories configuration and adding the Fedora stabilized
one.

This element:

- Downloads fedora stable repo .repo file under DIB_YUM_MINIMAL_BOOTSTRAP_REPOS to
  be used by yum-minimal in root.d.
- In cleanup.d, it removes existing .repo file from /etc/yum.repos.d and configures
  fedora stable repository config.

